     3→//! This module provides the data layer for the TUI, managing worker state,
     4→//! task information, cost analytics, and formatting data for display. It integrates with
     5→//! forge-core's StatusWatcher to provide real-time updates, forge-worker's
     6→//! tmux discovery for additional session information, the BeadManager
     7→//! for task queue data from monitored workspaces, forge-cost for cost analytics,
     8→//! LogWatcher for real-time log parsing, HealthMonitor for worker health tracking,
     9→//! and AlertManager for worker health alerts.
